New version for each product (Elasti X2, X3, compute, etc.) starting with 1 (0 is invalid indication)

Must be 0 for productionn-releasedd builds For debug, hotfix, release candidate etc. builds (which have a MINOR_VERSION) - First 28 bits are last 6 digits of owner's WWID without conversion from decimal to hex (e.g. 11305524->0x305524) - Lowest nibble (4 bits) is a user increment within the respective major/minor version For unreleased CI/CD builds (platform 0xC ~ 0xE): - All 32 bits will be the first 8 bits of the most recent commit SHA (sufficient to find a git commit in the history) in the repo of the subsystem where it was compiled For user unreleased builds (Platform 0xF): - First 28 bits are last 6 digits of owner's WWID without conversion from decimal to hex (e.g. 11305524->0x305524) - Lowest nibble (4 bits) is 0 if there are uncommitted changes in the repo or the first two MSB of the most recent commits SHA in the repo (this is NOT sufficient to find the commit in the history, but enough to identify recent commits through reflog etc.).
Power Limited Residency for GT - PL1 : Counter for time while GT is power limited (frequency is being throttled due to power limitations - either because of Package PL1 or Psys GPU PL1)
Power Limited Residency for GT - PL1 : Counter for time while GT is power limited (frequency is being throttled due to power limitations - either because of Package PL2 or Psys GPU PL2)
Power Limited Residency for GT - PL4 : Counter for time while GT is power limited (frequency is being throttled due to power limitations - because of Package PL4 Limit)

Thermal Limited Residency for GT : Counter for time while temperature limited (GT frequency is being throttled to meet temperature limits for any of the dies i.e. SoC top die, ADM die, GDDR device or VR)
ICCMAX Limited Residency for GT : Counter for time while current limited (frequency is being throttled because the requested GT frequency would result in exceeding VR Max. current )
VID Limited Residency for GT : Counter for time while VID limited (frequency is being throttled because the requested GT frequency would result in exceeding MAX VID limit)
Utilization Limited Residency for GT : Counter for time while utilization limited (GT frequency request < RPa - driver is requesting a lower frequency than it could if it wanted more performance)
Prochot Limited Residency for GT : Counter for time while limited due to Prochot (frequency requested for GT is not granted because of Prochot)
Psys_crit Limited Residency for GT : Counter for time while limited due to Prochot (frequency requested for GT is not granted because of Psys_crit)
Power Limited Residency for MEDIA - PL1 : Counter for time while MEDIA is power limited (frequency is being throttled due to power limitations - either because of Package PL1 or Psys GPU PL1)

VID Limited Residency for MEDIA : Counter for time while VID limited (frequency is being throttled because the requested MEDIA frequency would result in exceeding MAX VID limit)

Utilization Limited Residency for MEDIA : Counter for time while utilization limited (MEDIA frequency request < MPa - driver is requesting a lower frequency than it could if it wanted more performance)

Psys_crit Limited Residency for MEDIA : Counter for time while limited due to Prochot (frequency requested for MEDIA is not granted because of Psys_crit)
